				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\left({\mathrm{PFS}}_{\mathrm{ft}}\mathrm{PA}\right)$$\end{document}, weighted picture fuzzy soft power average WPFSftPA\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\left({\mathrm{WPFS}}_{\mathrm{ft}}\mathrm{PA}\right)$$\end{document} and ordered weighted picture fuzzy soft power average OWPFSftPA\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\left({\mathrm{OWPFS}}_{\mathrm{ft}}\mathrm{PA}\right)$$\end{document} aggregation operators. Moreover, we have introduced the notions for picture fuzzy soft power geometric PFSftPG\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\left({\mathrm{PFS}}_{\mathrm{ft}}\mathrm{PG}\right)$$\end{document}, weighted picture fuzzy soft power geometric WPFSftPG\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\left({\mathrm{WPFS}}_{\mathrm{ft}}\mathrm{PG}\right)$$\end{document} and ordered weighted picture fuzzy soft power geometric OWPFSftPG\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\left({\mathrm{OWPFS}}_{\mathrm{ft}}\mathrm{PG}\right)$$\end{document} aggregation operators. Furthermore, we have established the application of picture fuzzy soft power aggregation operators for the selection of thermal energy storage techniques. For this, we have developed a decision-making approach along with an explanatory example to show the effective use of the developed theory. Furthermore, a comparative analysis of the introduced work shows the advancement of developed notions.

sec.p:
