Power aggregation operators were introduced by Yager32 and if we ignore the support element, the power average reduces to a simple average. Also, if all the support is the same then the power average reduces to a simple average. Many developments have been made on this aggregation operator like Jiang et al.33 use the more generalized structure of intuitionistic fuzzy set to construct the thought of power aggregation operators. Also, Pythagorean fuzzy power aggregation operators were established by Wei et al.34.
